            , was indicted for <rs id="t17340424-5-off16" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17340424-5-off16" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17340424-5-off16" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing 22 yards of printed Linnen, val. 22 s. 15 yards of Printed Cotton, val. 30 s. 38 yards of Check, val. 38 s. 13 yards of blue Linnen-val. 13 s. 24 yards of Printed Linnen Hankerchiefs, val. 24 s. 22 yards of Muslin, val. 3 l. 6 s. 15 yards of Cambrick, val. 3 l. 36 Ells of Holland, val. 4 l. 10 s. 14 Ells of Nuns Holland, val. 28 s. 36 yards of Irish Linnen, val. 56 s. and 8 yards of Course Linnen Wrapper, val. 4 s. the Goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17340424-5-victim52" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Wingfield 
                        <interp inst="t17340424-5-victim52" type="surname" value="Wingfield"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17340424-5-victim52" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17340424-5-victim52" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17340424-5-off16 t17340424-5-victim52"></join>
